description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 29, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 29, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 1 for East, 5 for South, and 2 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/90291-61522-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [29 Votes, Common]
